      <li> The Mythical Man Month</li>
      <li> Agile Manifesto</li>
      <li> Getting Real</li>
      <li> Applied Cryptography</li>
      <li> How Buildings Learn  -- Stewart Brand</li>
      <li> Mental Models: Aligning Design Strategy with Human Behavior  -- Indi Young</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
